Chris,

My heat problem is a volume issue. I can barely keep my hands over the
outlets on the dash when the engine has heated up, but there is not enhough
volume to really do much more than keeping ice off the windshield.

My bus is a 74 - no 180 bent here. Obviously, there is less heat transferred
the more volume you push through, but for the short time my bilge blower was
working, I got a decent volume of nice warm (though not hot) air.

Marcus

